15:32.000 --> 15:33.000
- [laughs]

15:33.000 --> 15:34.070
- All right.

15:34.070 --> 15:36.000
Well, I've given them
enough time,

15:36.000 --> 15:38.100
so I'm gonna interrupt
whatever they're doing.

15:38.100 --> 15:39.830
- Uh-oh.
