15:39.830 --> 15:41.500
- There you are,
interrupting us again.

15:41.500 --> 15:44.899
Man, this is
the biggest trick we've had,

15:44.899 --> 15:47.330
and in my world,
bigger is always better.

15:47.330 --> 15:49.169
- You and me
