15:49.169 --> 15:50.169
- [laughs]

15:50.169 --> 15:51.230
And I'll also tell you

15:51.230 --> 15:54.200
that bigger is also
more difficult.

15:54.200 --> 15:55.029
- That's correct.

15:55.029 --> 15:57.169
- You can fool people
a lot easier

15:57.169 --> 15:58.899
with a small deck of cards...
- Sure.

15:58.899 --> 16:00.500
- Thank you can
with a big spectacle.

16:00.500 --> 16:02.230
- And it takes more people.
