16:02.230 --> 16:05.029
- Yeah, and you had
wonderful people assisting you,

16:05.029 --> 16:06.230
wonderful dancers.

16:06.230 --> 16:08.570
The whole production
is absolutely beautiful.

16:08.570 --> 16:11.230
You know, there's a technique
in magic,

16:11.230 --> 16:12.600
and I'm gonna say
the words here,

16:12.600 --> 16:15.100
because your use of it
is so good

16:15.100 --> 16:17.370
that I can almost give it away
without giving it away,

16:17.370 --> 16:20.899
because you've misdirected
from this principle so well.

16:20.899 --> 16:24.000
You're using black art,
