16:24.000 --> 16:29.330
and it's a way for the light
to hit the iris and confuse it

16:29.330 --> 16:31.370
so that people can become
invisible.

16:31.370 --> 16:34.070
It's really
a wonderful technique.

16:34.070 --> 16:36.529
The really crude way
