17:18.430 --> 17:20.368
- You entertained
all of us.

17:20.368 --> 17:22.200
- Thank you very much.
- Thank you so much.

17:22.200 --> 17:24.098
Greg Frewin!
- Thank you.

17:24.098 --> 17:25.670
- Thank you.

17:25.670 --> 17:27.670
[cheers and applause]

17:27.670 --> 17:29.069
We've got plenty more magic,

17:29.069 --> 17:32.069
including something special
from Penn and Teller.

