- Welcome back
to "Penn & Teller: Fool Us."

17:52.200 --> 17:55.069
Let's meet
our next potential fooler.

17:57.869 --> 17:59.329
- My name is Vinny Grosso.

17:59.329 --> 18:01.569
I perform a smart,
sophisticated,

18:01.569 --> 18:03.730
