18:37.200 --> 18:39.730
[cheers and applause]

18:39.730 --> 18:45.869
- Give it up for the
always-classy Vinny Grosso!

18:45.869 --> 18:47.900
[cheers and applause]
- Thank you.

18:47.900 --> 18:50.329
A magician wearing a tuxedo.

