a picky eater.

18:58.200 --> 19:00.900
Many people say I have
a problem.

19:00.900 --> 19:02.900
I like to think of it
as a gift.

19:02.900 --> 19:07.000
I have an acute,
superhuman-like sense of taste.

19:07.000 --> 19:10.700
I'll prove it
in the most scientific way

19:10.700 --> 19:12.369
a magician knows how:

19:12.369 --> 19:14.329
with a deck of cards.

19:14.329 --> 19:15.569
[laughter]

19:15.569 --> 19:17.599
And a volunteer.

19:17.599 --> 19:19.730
Choosing a volunteer,
there's an art to it.

19:19.730 --> 19:22.769
You need to find someone that
