19:22.769 --> 19:24.369
someone that won't upstage you.

19:24.369 --> 19:26.170
I found the perfect person
backstage.

19:26.170 --> 19:27.599
Please welcome Carrot Top.

19:27.599 --> 19:29.599
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.
[cheers and applause]

19:29.599 --> 19:31.029
Hi. Hello.

19:31.029 --> 19:32.900
How are you?
- Nice to meet you.

19:32.900 --> 19:35.029
[cheers and applause]

19:35.029 --> 19:37.200
Hello, buddy.
Good to see you.

19:37.200 --> 19:39.500
This is fun, fun, fun.

19:39.500 --> 19:41.029
- Carrot Top,
can you inspect these?

19:41.029 --> 19:42.099
Great. Thank you.

19:42.099 --> 19:43.000
Check 'em out.

19:43.000 --> 19:44.730
Make sure there's
nothing wrong with it.

