20:04.700 --> 20:05.700
- Let's see here.

20:05.700 --> 20:06.829
- Nothing there?

20:06.829 --> 20:07.930
- Cough real quick.

20:07.930 --> 20:09.730
- [laughs]
We'll get to that.

20:09.730 --> 20:11.069
- You look good.
