20:11.069 --> 20:12.369
You look clear.
- Great.

20:12.369 --> 20:14.369
I could be wearing a wire.

20:14.369 --> 20:16.069
You know, some sort of
signaling apparatus?

20:16.069 --> 20:17.400
- Yes, yes,
should I feel you up?

