with you.

20:37.230 --> 20:39.099
Uh, Carrot Top...

20:39.099 --> 20:40.000
- Yes.

20:40.000 --> 20:41.569
- You're gonna have
to vouch for them.

20:41.569 --> 20:44.099
- Okay.

20:44.099 --> 20:45.430
Do I stand here?
Stand here, yes?

20:45.430 --> 20:47.069
- Right over here.
- Over here, okay.

20:47.069 --> 20:49.730
Don't know what I'm doing.

20:49.730 --> 20:51.170
Oh, that's it! That--
Okay, good.

20:51.170 --> 20:52.200
That's it.

20:52.200 --> 20:53.000
Ah, man.

20:53.000 --> 20:57.099
[laughter and whistling]

20:57.099 --> 21:00.200
[cheers and applause]

21:04.099 --> 21:07.029
The water is very cold.
The water is very cold.

21:07.029 --> 21:08.529
[laughter]

21:08.529 --> 21:11.700
- Carrot Top.
- Yes? No!

21:11.700 --> 21:15.269
- Do you see anything funny--
let me rephrase that.

21:15.269 --> 21:16.900
Am I wearing a wire?

21:16.900 --> 21:19.029
- No, you're not wearing--
no, I don't believe so, no.

21:19.029 --> 21:22.029
I feel like Carrot Bottom
