- No, you can use these
right over here.

21:52.900 --> 21:54.170
- That's great.
That's great.

21:54.170 --> 21:55.829
- Can you check those out?

21:55.829 --> 21:57.200
- Check these out?
- Yeah.

21:57.200 --> 21:59.000
Make sure there's nothing wrong
