what your card is,

22:22.930 --> 22:26.000
with the exception
of my incredible sense of taste.

22:26.000 --> 22:28.099
So I'm going to stick
my tongue out,

22:28.099 --> 22:31.829
and I'd like you tap
the card--just the tip--

22:31.829 --> 22:33.029
on my tongue.

22:33.029 --> 22:37.000
[laughter]

22:38.730 --> 22:41.599
- Should it--should it go back
in its holding spot?

22:41.599 --> 22:43.569
- With my acute sense
of taste...

22:43.569 --> 22:44.730
- It seemed easiest.

22:44.730 --> 22:46.900
- I can tell that your card
is red. Am I right?

22:46.900 --> 22:48.000
- Uh, yes.

22:48.000 --> 22:49.000
- Of course I am.

22:49.000 --> 22:50.000
I get it, though,

22:50.000 --> 22:51.099
It could have been
a lucky guess.

22:51.099 --> 22:52.099
Tap it again.

22:52.099 --> 22:54.099
- Okay.

22:54.099 --> 22:56.430
You have a beautiful tongue,
