23:08.930 --> 23:10.170
[laughter]

23:10.170 --> 23:14.000
- Carrot Top, with my acute,
superhuman-like sense of taste,

23:14.000 --> 23:16.170
I can tell that your card
is not just red,

23:16.170 --> 23:17.430
not only a diamond,

23:17.430 --> 23:19.869
