of diamonds.

23:19.869 --> 23:21.170
[cheers and applause]

23:21.170 --> 23:22.869
- You're right!

23:22.869 --> 23:24.000
That's pretty good.

23:24.000 --> 23:25.529
That's pretty good.

23:25.529 --> 23:27.900
- Ladies and gentlemen,
Carrot Top.

