[laughs nervously]

24:04.869 --> 24:07.069
There we go. That's better.

24:07.069 --> 24:08.930
That's much better.

24:08.930 --> 24:13.269
Um, and are you hoping
that by being naked,

24:13.269 --> 24:15.069
