everybody knows that from
police television shows,

25:25.000 --> 25:27.099
and adding that in
is really nice.

25:27.099 --> 25:29.200
This whole thing
is perfectly justified.

25:29.200 --> 25:30.200
It's really great.

25:30.200 --> 25:31.230
I also want to make clear--

25:31.230 --> 25:32.930
