28:05.200 --> 28:06.000
[bell ringing]

28:06.000 --> 28:08.369
Initially, magic found me.

28:08.369 --> 28:09.869
I was in the second grade,

28:09.869 --> 28:12.170
and a teacher assigned
a take-home project

28:12.170 --> 28:14.500
which was basically an old trick
that magicians do

28:14.500 --> 28:16.000
known as the Cups and Balls.

28:16.000 --> 28:18.029
Once I learned how
to do that trick,

28:18.029 --> 28:19.700
I was hooked.

28:19.700 --> 28:23.069
Like any art, I think magic
adds a beauty to the world.

28:23.069 --> 28:25.529
If it allows audiences
to escape,

28:25.529 --> 28:27.400
that's a pretty major thing.

28:27.400 --> 28:30.000
Every artist has
an inspiration,

28:30.000 --> 28:33.400
