No, that's not the trick.

29:23.269 --> 29:26.230
Tonight we're traveling
through another dimension.

29:26.230 --> 29:27.730
Oh, yeah.

29:27.730 --> 29:30.029
A dimension not only
of sight, sound, and mind

29:30.029 --> 29:33.430
but also of illusion.

29:38.529 --> 29:40.329
[laughter]
Yeah.

29:40.329 --> 29:44.500
[applause]

29:44.500 --> 29:47.599
