29:59.269 --> 30:02.269
This idea
has always fascinated me.

30:02.269 --> 30:04.569
You see, if I could actually
control the flow of time,

30:04.569 --> 30:07.000
I could perform
some great magic.

30:07.000 --> 30:10.069
Now, you may find a better use
for stopping time

30:10.069 --> 30:11.329
other than a trick,

30:11.329 --> 30:13.569
although right now, the only
thing that I can think about

30:13.569 --> 30:15.670
is how to create
a better mystery.

30:15.670 --> 30:18.029
Alyson, would you please
join me center stage

30:18.029 --> 30:20.170
as the audience gives you
a thunderous round of applause?

30:20.170 --> 30:21.700
[cheers and applause]

30:21.700 --> 30:23.029
Very nice to meet you, Alyson.

30:23.029 --> 30:24.230
- Nice to meet you.

30:24.230 --> 30:26.000
- Alyson?
- Yes.

30:26.000 --> 30:28.430
- Here, here is what
you will be in charge of.

30:28.430 --> 30:29.430
- Okay.

30:29.430 --> 30:32.329
- The black bag.

30:32.329 --> 30:36.200
Please hold on to it like so,
like I'm holding it.

30:36.200 --> 30:37.500
- Okay.
- There you go.

30:37.500 --> 30:39.700
- Just take a peek inside,
seeing that it's empty.

30:39.700 --> 30:41.670
And then hold it
all the way to your right,

30:41.670 --> 30:44.099
just with your right hand
so I can't reach inside the bag.

30:44.099 --> 30:45.200
Yeah, all the way out.

30:45.200 --> 30:46.900
That way, I can't get
anywhere near it.

30:46.900 --> 30:50.200
Now, Alyson, here is
what I am in charge of.

30:50.200 --> 30:51.170
- Oh.

30:51.170 --> 30:52.700
- The egg.

