Alyson, my goal
is to get the egg from here

30:54.730 --> 30:57.200
to inside that bag
without you even knowing it,

30:57.200 --> 31:00.430
a feat that's much easier
to accomplish if I...

31:00.430 --> 31:02.930
[warbling]

31:02.930 --> 31:05.069
[laughter]

31:07.930 --> 31:09.769
Were to stop the flow
of time.

31:09.769 --> 31:11.230
[laughter]

31:11.230 --> 31:14.430
Now, to you, it may have
seemed like nothing happened,

31:14.430 --> 31:16.000
although while you were
frozen in time--

31:16.000 --> 31:18.200
and you were,
except for Alyson--

31:18.200 --> 31:21.099
I managed to put the egg--

31:21.099 --> 31:23.430
I'll take the bag,
Alyson, please.

31:23.430 --> 31:24.599
Thank you.

31:24.599 --> 31:27.430
The egg inside the bag.

31:27.430 --> 31:28.430
audience: Oh!

31:28.430 --> 31:33.099
[applause]

31:33.099 --> 31:35.569
Perhaps I can use
this same method

31:35.569 --> 31:36.900
in order to make it vanish.

31:36.900 --> 31:39.170
Alyson, please. You can
still feel the egg, yes?

31:39.170 --> 31:40.269
Yeah?
- Yes.

31:40.269 --> 31:41.269
- That is until...

31:41.269 --> 31:42.529
[warbling]

31:42.529 --> 31:45.869
[laughter]

31:45.869 --> 31:49.869
It disappears,
leaving nothing but the bag.

31:49.869 --> 31:52.200
You see, if you weren't
suspended in time,

31:52.200 --> 31:55.730
you would have seen that I
removed the egg from the bag

31:55.730 --> 31:59.170
and put it back inside
my jacket pocket.

31:59.170 --> 32:00.769
Any questions?

32:00.769 --> 32:03.869
[applause]

32:03.869 --> 32:05.230
Alyson, you're doing great.

32:05.230 --> 32:07.099
One last time, hold on
to the bag like so.

32:07.099 --> 32:09.029
- Okay.
- Just take a peek inside,

32:09.029 --> 32:10.069
seeing that it's empty.

32:10.069 --> 32:11.829
And then hold it all the way
to your right,

32:11.829 --> 32:12.869
just with your right hand,

32:12.869 --> 32:15.170
so I can't reach
inside the bag.

32:15.170 --> 32:19.069
The egg, all the way
