32:19.069 --> 32:21.700
Once again,
the trickery takes place...

32:21.700 --> 32:22.869
[warbling]

32:22.869 --> 32:25.769
[laughter]

32:25.769 --> 32:28.170
During the suspension
of time.

32:29.569 --> 32:31.329
The proof?

32:31.329 --> 32:34.569
Yeah, the proof
is completely clear.

32:34.569 --> 32:35.730
You know, Alyson.
Go ahead.

32:35.730 --> 32:36.730
Give it a shake.

32:36.730 --> 32:37.829
I'll let you do the honor.

32:37.829 --> 32:39.099
Reach your hand
inside the bag

32:39.099 --> 32:40.369
and remove the egg.

32:40.369 --> 32:41.869
- What?

32:41.869 --> 32:43.099
- It worked!

32:43.099 --> 32:45.099
[cheers and applause]

32:45.099 --> 32:46.829
It worked.

32:48.529 --> 32:50.200
- That was crazy.

32:50.200 --> 32:51.269
[applause]

32:51.269 --> 32:53.200
- Now, some of you may feel

32:53.200 --> 32:54.869
the pausing of time
is just an illusion.

32:54.869 --> 32:57.029
But it's not the pausing of time
that's the illusion,

32:57.029 --> 33:01.369
but time itself
is the illusion,

33:01.369 --> 33:03.029
as you will notice
that the sand of time

33:03.029 --> 33:04.569
is completely gone.

33:04.569 --> 33:05.930
[audience exclaims]

33:05.930 --> 33:07.730
Alyson, if I may,
I'll take the egg, please.

33:07.730 --> 33:09.170
Thank you.

33:09.170 --> 33:14.099
After all, the concept of time,
it's a human invention.

33:14.099 --> 33:15.529
[objects clicking together]

33:15.529 --> 33:17.170
A concept
that was given birth to

33:17.170 --> 33:19.569
