of life...

33:19.569 --> 33:20.829
[piano music]

33:20.829 --> 33:22.730
Itself.

33:24.700 --> 33:27.700
[cheers and applause]

33:31.700 --> 33:33.700
Thank you so much.
- Thank you!

33:33.700 --> 33:36.200
- The question still exists,
