Now, this bacon has
a strong smell to it,

37:45.869 --> 37:47.500
and I rubbed my fingers on it,

37:47.500 --> 37:50.030
and then when I came up and
you knew what card you picked,

37:50.030 --> 37:51.730
I rubbed it
all over the card.

37:51.730 --> 37:54.769
Now I could put that card
anywhere in the deck I want.

